  "slug": "mo-structures",
  "title": "Mo' Structures (NeoForge/Fabric)",
  "description": "Mo' Structures is Fabric's best structure mod, carefully designed to enrich your world!",
  "body": "<p>Starting in 1.21, this mod requires <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/architectury-api\" rel=\"nofollow\">Architectury API</a>!</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/f4C0bxb/4e21473c381762c7fa08cea89159b7dd4299bb01da39a3ee5e6b4b0d3255bfef95601890afd80709da39a3ee5e6b4b0d3255bfef95601890afd80709365200db273d9a080f0768875cf62c00-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1120\" height=\"121\" /><br /></strong></span></h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Discover exciting structures with fun mini-dungeons and integrated lore!</strong></span></h4><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><h1></h1></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Do you want&nbsp; to run through dark mazes, explore floating castles, and fight evil pillagers? Want to keep a simple vanilla world with no new blocks or items?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><em>Then get this mod ASAP!</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Our goal is to be the best structure mod in the Fabric ecosystem!&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mo' Structures is carefully designed to bring interesting lore to your Minecraft World.&nbsp; We focus on the RPG aspect of your world rather than an aesthetic one, by focusing on user's decisions that affect their gameplay. It's simple- by introducing structures that can fit almost any need a player might be interested in, we allow them to create their own survival experience. Using loot tables, advancements, jigsaws, unused bosses, and more, we are able to bring thousands of new experiences that will make this mod be a must-download for every mod gameplay.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This mod is for Fabric Mod Loader. I will not be porting the mod to Forge, If you are a Modder and would like to make a Forge version, feel free to contact me.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>PLEASE MORE FEEDBACK!! WE WANT TO HEAR FROM YOU, SO GO TO OUR DISCORD OR COMMENT ON HERE!</strong></span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Here are some pictures of the mod:</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">JUNGLE PYRAMID</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/TYpQgWF/2020-05-06-17-07-15.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1124\" height=\"615\" /></p>\n<p>VILLAGER MARKET</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/yQB2D17/2020-11-25-14-44-11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1124\" height=\"615\" /></p>\n<p>PILLAGER FACTORY</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DY3K5nf/2020-11-25-14-46-44.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">THE CASTLE IN THE SKY</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/TgZYMBk/2020-05-09-14-59-00.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1124\" height=\"615\" /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">BARNHOUSE</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vjmyZFd/2020-04-21-13-22-37.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1165\" height=\"638\" /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">KILLER BUNNY CASTLE</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qmjbhqJ/2021-02-13-21-41-35.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1126\" height=\"616\" /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Go to our wiki to see more structures or download the mod today!</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>WIKI:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures/wiki\">https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures/wiki</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>BUGS AND SOURCE:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures\">https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><strong>Keep up with development:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures/projects\">https://github.com/franiscoder/mostructures/projects</a></strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>DISCORD:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Join me in my discord!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/uvqTeQzQXK\">https://discord.gg/uvqTeQzQXK</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>PROGRESS:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Check out our progress on github:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/frqnny/mostructures/projects\">https://github.com/frqnny/mostructures/projects</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>CREDITS:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>ffrann - author</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>halotroop - 1.15.2 backport</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>thank you to the world gen discord for helping me greatly on structure generation, and thank you to fabric for making a platform to make mods!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em><strong>CHECK OUT MY NEW MOD, CHRISTMAS SPIRIT REWOVEN!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cspirit\">https://modrinth.com/mod/cspirit</a></strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cspirit\">&nbsp;</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>",
